metadata.name: My Faith - Space #1/438
metadata.description:
We are here to celebrate your victories and achievements, to admire your perseverance and determination. We are here to see you at the top and also to see you fall.
In life, only those who take risks and are capable of appreciating the abysses and the great heights, are those who triumph. And you are one of them.
With your faith, you will maintain balance when darkness looms and you will stand when the winds lash. And when you reach the top again, you will understand that true success is having survived the journey while appreciating the view.
